jinngine.physics
Class Body

java.lang.Object
  jinngine.physics.Body
Direct Known Subclasses:
Box, CompositeBody, Cylinder, Dome, Ellipsoid, NullBody, Octahedron, Sphere, Tetrahedron
public abstract class Body
extends java.lang.Object

Abstract class representing a rigid body. This class implements most functionality needed to handle bodies in a simulation. It is required that new body types inherit from this Body class.
